msgid ""
"<br/>Clear, consistent communication drives success. We prioritize open "
"dialogue, ensuring alignment with your goals and seamless collaboration "
"throughout every project."
msgstr ""
"<br/>Komunikasi yang jernih & konsisten mendorong kesuksesan. Kami "
"memprioritaskan dialog terbuka, memastikan penyelarasan dengan tujuan-tujuan "
"Anda dan kolaborasi mulus di setiap project yang tersedia."

#. module: theme_paptic
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_paptic.s_cover
msgid "<br/>Offering tailored strategies to drive growth and success."
msgstr ""
"<br/>Menawarkan strategi-strategi yang dibuat khusus untuk mendorong "
"pertumbuhan dan kesuksesan."

#. module: theme_paptic
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_paptic.s_image_text
msgid ""
"<br/>Our code is built for performance, scalability, and reliability. With "
"meticulous attention to detail, we create clean, maintainable, and efficient "
"solutions that power your business forward."
msgstr ""
"<br/>Code kami dibuat untuk performa, scalability, dan keandalanan. Dengan "
"perhatian ke detail yang seksama, kami membuat solusi yang jernih, "
"berkelanjutan, dan efisien yang mendorong bisnis Anda maju ke depan.."

